colleague, Bruce Kimball,

00:25:28.000 --> 00:25:31.360
co-director of the Harvard
Law School History Project

00:25:31.360 --> 00:25:36.730
and co-author of a new book,
On the Battlefield of Merit,

00:25:36.730 --> 00:25:41.560
which is the first of two
volumes, a new critical history

00:25:41.560 --> 00:25:43.680
of Harvard Law School.

00:25:43.680 --> 00:25:46.240
I just tell you those two
volumes-- those are not books

00:25:46.240 --> 00:25:47.560
that you can't put down.

00:25:47.560 --> 00:25:49.340
Those are books
you can't pick up.

00:25:49.340 --> 00:25:51.940
